  <brief_title>Japanese Efficacy and Safety Study of Enoxaparin in Patients With Curative Abdominal Cancer Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter, Randomized, Open-label Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Enoxaparin Sodium (RP54563) 20mg Bid for 14 Days for Prevention of Venous Thromboembolism in Patients With Curative Abdominal Cancer Surgery. Physical Prophylaxis Only Arm [Intermittent Pneumatic Compression (IPC)] Will be Used as an Indicator of Event Rates.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
