  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to evaluate the effects of enoxaparin on venous
      thromboembolism incidence and bleeding rate (major and minor bleeding) in patients undergoing
      curative abdominal cancer surgery. The secondary objective is evaluate the incidence of
      adverse events of enoxaparin in these patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
